          "reviewBody": "Presidium School is a very famous school. This school can been seen from the main road itself. It's near Krishna Chowk. This school has all the facilities like Digital classroom, library, Science lab, computer lab all at state of art building. Students here are very secure as they are every strict with their security. Admission here is very easy as they don't have much students as per their Brand name. Teachers here are well qualified, earlier management had salary issues now its solved. They also has a play school in the name of Mother's Pride, which grooms your child.",
